$AMD (Jan 22, 2026-daily chart update)

See You at All-Time High

Last April to May 2025, most "furus" (influencers with huge followers) were predicting a recession and the start of a major bear market. That turned out to be the perfect window for me to start loading up on $AMD — though I didn't nail the absolute bottom at around $76.

For me, position sizing matters far more than perfectly timing the bottom. I kept adding shares along the way and shared all my buy orders with my Tier 3 subscribers. Our final buy was at $198.Some people chose to follow my lead — including my best friends — while others kept criticizing $AMD. I've now nearly completed my 6-month accumulation plan, holding more than 24,000 shares.

On the daily chart, every time the red ribbon emerges, it tends to unfold and propel the stock higher. Are you still waiting for that $162–$170 gap fill that most of those big-account furus keep talking about? They've become my contrarian signals — and every time I bet against them, I make money!

